| Trait visible | Yes | No |
| IDE support | Full | Full |

## When to Use Derive

Use `#[derive(Model)]` when:
- Building standard TUI applications
- You want reduced boilerplate
- State change tracking is beneficial

Use manual implementation when:
- You need custom trait behavior
